link:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 26, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dhb1665702759914.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dhb1665702759914.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dhb1665702759914.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dhb1665702759914\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Operation called by the SAX parser when it issues a warning.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104dhb1665702759914_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__codeblock_oms_2g4_hwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation WARNING\n  params\n     string List: in\n  endparams\n\nImplement your code here\n\nend; WARNING operation</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__section_bq5_fg4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d336599e53\">Parameters</h2>\n<dl class=\"dl\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__dl_ikf_cc4_hwb\">\n<dt class=\"dt dlterm\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">List</var></dt>\n<dd class=\"dd\">Associated list identifying the location and nature of the error. The identifiers can\n              be:<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__ul_jwl_cc4_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__li_d48380e1_d48381e1_d48382e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">LINE</code>—line number within the\n                XML document where the error occurred</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__li_d48383e1_d48384e1_d48385e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">COLUMN</code>—column number within\n                the XML document where the error occurred</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__li_d48386e1_d48387e1_d48388e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">MESSAGE</code>—error message issued\n                by the parser. If provided by the SAX parser, the following may also be in the list:\n                  <ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__ul_kwl_cc4_hwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__li_d48389e1_d48390e1_d48391e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">PUBLICID</code>—public identifier\n                    of an XML entity</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__li_d48392e1_d48393e1_d48394e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">SYSTEMID</code>—local identifier\n                    of an XML entity</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul></dd>\n</dl>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__section_kc5_ng4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d336599e102\">Return Values</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__p_d137267e1_d137268e1_d137269e1\">If the operation returns a non-negative value, parsing\n        continues.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__section_fgl_pg4_hwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d336599e111\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dhb1665702759914__p_d137273e1_d137274e1_d137275e1\">Use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">getitem</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">/id</code> to retrieve individual items from this list.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526810\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526810\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "WARNING Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Operation called by the SAX parser when it issues a warning. Explain this code operation WARNING params string List: in endparams Implement your code here end; WARNING operation Copy Parameters List Associated list identifying the location and nature of the error. The identifiers can be: LINE —line number within the XML document where the error occurred COLUMN —column number within the XML document where the error occurred MESSAGE —error message issued by the parser. If provided by the SAX parser, the following may also be in the list: PUBLICID —public identifier of an XML entity SYSTEMID —local identifier of an XML entity Return Values If the operation returns a non-negative value, parsing continues. Description Use getitem /id to retrieve individual items from this list. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}